# Treasure Island Game
# Based on story telling concepts like dungeon and dragaons or old story books
# Used ascii art
# Used all concepts learned on the first three days to make the project
# Used concepts like input, if else, nested if else, mathematical operators, logical operators
# Program uses pre-completed story and asks user for input to proceed in the game
# print(r''' some code ''') indicates a raw string and characters like \n or \t are treated as literal characters

